53
00:02:20,720 --> 00:02:20,720
And you can see that the

54
00:02:20,720 --> 00:02:20,720
universe is a little bit more hot.

55
00:02:20,720 --> 00:02:24,380
and they're redshifted by roughly about a factor of 1,000,

56
00:02:25,080 --> 00:02:27,860
that effectively means that the temperature

57
00:02:29,060 --> 00:02:32,600
that we would see in the sky

58
00:02:32,600 --> 00:02:35,360
is about 1,000 times lower,

59
00:02:36,240 --> 00:02:38,680
or it appears to be about 1,000 times lower

60
00:02:38,680 --> 00:02:39,940
than the actual temperature

61
00:02:39,940 --> 00:02:42,280
