686
00:27:00,020 --> 00:27:01,980
but I just point this out to you

687
00:27:01,980 --> 00:27:04,300
as a sort of mnemonic

688
00:27:04,300 --> 00:27:08,980
for the fact that the net charge

689
00:27:08,980 --> 00:27:12,340
of the universe is zero.

690
00:27:12,500 --> 00:27:14,980
Or at least it looks to be zero.

691
00:27:15,340 --> 00:27:18,020
Any place where we find positive charges,

692
00:27:18,120 --> 00:27:19,260
