693
00:27:19,400 --> 00:27:21,140
And we don't find any large-scale

694
00:27:21,140 --> 00:27:24,500
concentrations of positive

695
00:27:24,500 --> 00:27:25,460
or negative charge.

696
00:27:25,720 --> 00:27:27,600
They seem to cancel out pretty well.

697
00:27:28,040 --> 00:27:28,460
Okay.

